{"tid":2228609,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"習皇帝畫像做封面當「賀禮」 法媒特輯諷永恆中華帝國專制","createTime":"2020-10-03T17:04:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T04:09:29.000Z","uid":240362,"like":405,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"c2cfde8cd6a9b41a14bd864584f19e27c3e6b567","tid":2228609,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T17:04:19.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情肆虐全球，每日都有數以萬計人士染疫，甚至死亡，令歐美各地出現反中情緒。法國媒體《新觀察家》（Le Nouvel Observateur）更選擇在中共建政71周年這周，推出題為「中國，永恆王朝：沉浸2000年的權力」的深度特輯，封面是龍袍加身、穩坐皇位的中共總書記習近平，以諷刺今天的中國已重回帝國專制。<br />\n<br />\n「這是諷刺畫嗎？還是西方對中國魯莽崛起恐懼的投射？」《新觀察家》最近一期的深度特輯，以22篇深度分析專文，探討中國2000年帝國主義思想在政治實踐中的根源，開門見山在介紹文字中已表示：「習近平稱帝讓世界意識到中原王朝還沒消失，它找到新的存在方式了。」<br />\n<br />\n「在20世紀，中國崛起的民族主義成為了科學怪人（Frankenstein）般的產物：一個以一切手段尋求權力的國族，並在驅逐民主概念後，企圖以中國『天下』取代現今多邊國家競逐的世界。」《新觀察家》寫道。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201003/7NXONUPGANAP7AJYG24ZRXHBDY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201003%2F7NXONUPGANAP7AJYG24ZRXHBDY%2F&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdr%2BiaDmtBxIfZa%2Bp1tlHcc8%3D&h=3c2788d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201003%2F7NXONUPGANAP7AJYG24ZRXHBDY%2F&h=0a927177\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201003/7NXONUPGANAP7AJYG24ZRXHBDY/</a>"},{"pid":"f2ba3fae77aa836ecc1a78f3d9c238f77b74e579","tid":2228609,"uid":14449,"like":184,"dislike":2,"score":182,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T17:09:06.000Z","msg":"法國佬識得「天下」呢個concept<br />\n認真行得好得前<br />\n分分鐘班左膠仲屌人racist"},{"pid":"2e7c918237a2f1970d9b2a1942074ffe64f8dae7","tid":2228609,"uid":2054,"like":127,"dislike":0,"score":127,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T17:14:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180227/640_12ab9b4292c377d90f4a7c47ae3fb02c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180227%2F640_12ab9b4292c377d90f4a7c47ae3fb02c.jpg&h=81608